    IDispatcher, IEnvironment, IInterpreter, IInterpreterContext, IInterpreterSetters, IPropertiesExtender, ITransformInterpreter, IThreadResolver

    public class JuniconInterpreter
extends TransformInterpreter
    JuniconInterpreter implements a transformational interpreter tailored to transform Unicon programs into Groovy or Java. It can be customized here for specific setters for dependency injection.
